snippet.textDisplay: Actually, no. First of all, zombies arenʻt technically caused by viruses or even bacteria, theyʻre a fictional horror creature which are evil spirits possessing dead bodies. Secondly, even if we go by the incorrect definition of zombies that most modern movies and video games use, still no, because the coronavirus is not the type of thing that would cause such symptoms. “Zombies” of that kind would be caused by a mutation of mycobacterium leprae, also called Hansenʻs disease or as you probably know it from the Bible, leprosy.
